Text: You're welcome, my friend! And sorry for the delay!
Nepotu, you've done this community a great favor by keeping up this work - and it's damn good work too; don't let anyone tell you otherwise. Have a happy holiday. Cheers, bro! Yippie!
In my country it's 25th now, so thank you for this christmas gift and MERRY CHRISTMAS to you Nepotu !!  ^o^
Thank you my dear friends from all over the world! Your words means a lot to me. I wish you all a Happy hollyday and Merry Christmas, whoever and wherever you are!
